{"tid":2236281,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"德國跟隊？德國巴伐利亞邦議會成立友台小組","createTime":"2020-10-09T11:00:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-09T11:46:41.000Z","uid":14494,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"00047a760dc30faf7c002ee6d0d49415fa8f464d","tid":2236281,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T11:00:01.000Z","msg":"（中央社記者林育立柏林8日專電）德國巴伐利亞邦（Bayern）議會今天成立友台小組，成員來自朝野各黨派，未來將全力推動對台關係。<br />\n<br />\n「巴伐利亞友台小組」（Freundeskreis Bayern-Taiwan）成立大會今晚在巴伐利亞邦議會舉行，執政的基社黨（CSU）、自由選民黨（Freie W&auml;hler）及在野的社民黨（SPD）、自民黨（FDP）、綠黨（Die Gr&uuml;nen）均有議員出席，駐德代表謝志偉也應邀致詞。<br />\n<br />\n主持成立大會的邦議會副議長林德斯巴哈（Markus Rinderspacher）致詞時表示，去年11月訪台時對台灣印象深刻，當下就決定在返國後成立友台小組，期待小組能持續運作下去，不因議員離任而中斷。<br />\n<br />\n巴伐利亞友台小組是邦議員自發成立的開放性團體，多位議員今天對中國軍機持續擾台相當關切。<br />\n<br />\n林德斯巴哈指出，友台小組的成立宗旨是支持民主台灣，未來將結合跨黨派力量，協助推動議會和姐妺市的交流，深化台灣與巴伐利亞的友好關係。<br />\n<br />\n巴伐利亞邦議會近來對台灣友好，歐洲委員會今年年初才通過決議案，支持台灣以觀察員身分參與世界衛生大會（WHA）。<br />\n<br />\n位於南部的巴伐利亞是德國面積最大的邦，也是製造業重鎮，擁有西門子（Siemens）、BMW、奧迪（Audi）、愛迪達（Adidas）等跨國企業，與台灣經貿關係相當密切。<br />\n<br />\n此外，巴伐利亞有22所大學與台灣的30所大學簽訂交流計畫，史坦堡縣（Starnberg）並與新北市和花蓮縣結為姊妹縣。（編輯：徐崇哲）1091009<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202010090013.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Ffirstnews%2F202010090013.aspx&d=6zgGjWaceJ4ICz2LU8gYzkx5KyfgaA76LUEybGJClr4%3D&h=2829a78e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202010090013.aspx</a>"},{"pid":"6ace48b1ad4bac18dd27b4d4c8080efee9f15716","tid":2236281,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T11:01:17.000Z","msg":"一邊屌肥婆奶共 咁你簽左未呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n德國政府官方聯署：夠數德國就一定要喺國會討論制裁中國<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2229090\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2229090</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e01888aa91076874d551fcc485bfaebcd52c772a","tid":2236281,"uid":306914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T11:01:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11364ba6a2be936beb54582eb353915724ebd293","tid":2236281,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T11:02:59.000Z","msg":"齊賀國慶<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fd5b9fe9913b9672e5a26a73bc651a6601d470e","tid":2236281,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6ace48b1ad4bac18dd27b4d4c8080efee9f15716","tid":2236281,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T11:01:17.000Z","msg":"一邊屌肥婆奶共 咁你簽左未呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n德國政府官方聯署：夠數德國就一定要喺國會討論制裁中國<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2229090\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2229090</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T11:12:05.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">肥婆係CDU<br />\n但係德國D企業係哂巴伐利亞</span>"},{"pid":"d1e7f37afc83059d9a8281db1bd6d22b67c8ab48","tid":2236281,"uid":340040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T11:13:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c33ca67c163492dcda09540bf77aa7bd99a87337","tid":2236281,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T11:46:41.000Z","msg":"推"}]}